{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/create-a-bootstrap-headline","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"bootstrap","demoType":null,"title":"Kreiranje naslova Bootstrap-a","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Hajde da nešto napravimo od nule kako bismo vežbali naše znanje HTML-a, CSS-a i Bootstrap-a.</p>\n<p>Napradićemo jQuery Playground, koji ćemo uskoro koristiti u našim jQuery izazovima.</p>\n<p>Da počnemo, kreirajte <code>h3</code> element sa tekstom <code>jQuery Playground</code>.</p>\n<p>Stilizujte svoj <code>h3</code> element klasom Bootstrap-a <code>text-primary</code>, i centrirajte ga koristeći klasu Bootstrap-a <code>text-center</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aec908846","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16812,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/create-a-bootstrap-headline"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da dodate <code>h3</code> element na svoju stranicu.</p>","testString":"assert.lengthOf(document.querySelectorAll('h3'),1);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš <code>h3</code> element treba da ima zatvarajući tag.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code,/<\\/h3>/g);\r\nassert.match(code,/<h3/g);\r\nassert.equal( code.match(/<\\/h3>/g).length , code.match(/<h3/g).length);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš <code>h3</code> element treba da bude stilizovan korišćenjem klase <code>text-primary</code></p>","testSt